text: "Déjà Vu" was released on April 1, 2021 on Geffen and Interscope records by singer-songwriter Olivia Rodrigo, the title of his own Deja Vu comment written and recorded in 2020 for releasing Deja Vu on April 1. It went to number 3 in the United States, Australia, New Zealand, Malaysia, Singapore and made number 2 in Ireland. It was written by Taylor Swift and St. Vincent. == References == Category:2021 songs Category:Pop rock songs Category:Art pop songs Category:Indie pop songs Category:Psychedelic pop songs Category:Olivia Rodrigo songs
